#String tooltip
This bot mines rock tiles in a selected area. You will be asked to select an area for mining at bot start. The bot will systematically mine each rock tile in the area, automatically chip boulders that appear, restore stamina when needed, and handle mining supports health monitoring. The bot will stop if enemy appears or mining support structure becomes too damaged.
